<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q21_v4" title="Radicales_equivalentes_contexto_intensidad" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En un circuito eléctrico, después de realizar ciertos cálculos, se obtiene que la intensidad de corriente es 
      <m:math>
        <m:mfrac>
          <m:msqrt>
            <m:mn>27</m:mn>
          </m:msqrt>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
        </m:mfrac>
      </m:math>
      amperes. Para comparar con otros valores medidos, se desea escribir esta intensidad con la raíz lo más simplificada posible. ¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa la misma intensidad?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, por lo tanto <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:msqrt><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. La opción A vale <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, que no es igual a la intensidad dada.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:msqrt>
            <m:mn>9</m:mn>
          </m:msqrt>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:msqrt><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. En cambio, <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, esta opción no representa la misma intensidad.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:msqrt>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          </m:msqrt>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:msqrt><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. La expresión equivalente es <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La intensidad dada se simplifica como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:msqrt><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. Si fuera igual a <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math>, entonces se tendría <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, pero al elevar ambos valores al cuadrado resulta <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por eso esta opción no es equivalente.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso de la simplificación del radical</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Escribir la expresión dada</strong></p>
            <p>La intensidad es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:msqrt><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> amperes.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Descomponer 27 para simplificar la raíz</strong></p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>27</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, entonces</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Reemplazar en la fracción</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:msqrt><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Simplificar el factor común</strong></p>
            <p>En el numerador y en el denominador aparece el factor <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math>, por lo que</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 5: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión simplificada es <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>, que corresponde a la alternativa C.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La misma intensidad, escrita con la raíz lo más simplificada posible, es <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math> amperes.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>